overview: Na-young, a job-seeking student, receives a letter of acceptance from a venture company, Log M, and calls for joy. Bonus 400%! Even the friendly smile of CEO Hoonnam. The only job assigned to Na-young is managing the power of the company server or making coffee. Na-young, a new employee who did not want to lose the good fortune that had come so much, became a member of the company by enduring the sexual harassment of the lesbian team leader Mi-ran. She appeals to her sexy side and follows her to the reception desk for success... What is the true identity of Jun-seo, a young venture capitalist, and the shocking identity of Rogue M?
title: New Female Employee
